parameters.completionMessage:
=Thank you for submitting an appointment request. A confirmation of this request will be sent to your inbox. I'll get back to you shortly with a confirmation of the appointment.

Here is the summary of the appointment request.

Name: {{ $('Get Form Values').item.json.name }}
Date & Time: {{ DateTime.fromISO($('Get Form Values').item.json.dateTime).format('EEE, dd MMM @ t') }}
Enquiry: {{ $('Get Form Values').item.json.enquiry.trim() }}

